## ## 2014 ### We have been challenging rock ridges and walls since our founding in 2014 using alpine style with our ambition.
*** *** *** *** *** *** *** Safety first and thorough basics. *** *** Enforcing self rescue to help our members by ourself. *** *** Founder, former rescue team in Nagano ***
## Organization 1. Climing division. 2. Traverse division. 2251510 Limit of members is 25 in total(15 for Climing, 10 for Traverse), in order to activate activities. ## Activities - Training on mountains in Kansai region every mounth. - Having monthly meeting at our office, reporting activities and planning. - 11 Having activities mostly on Japan Alps once a month or every two months. - Having training and activities not only on weekends but also on weekdays. 2014

We have been challenging rock ridges and walls since our founding in 2014 using alpine style with our ambition.





Safety first and thorough basics.
Enforcing self rescue to help our members by ourself.
Founder, former rescue team in Nagano

Organization

  1. Climing division.
  2. Traverse division.
    2251510

    Limit of members is 25 in total(15 for Climing, 10 for Traverse), in order to activate activities.

Activities


  • Training on mountains in Kansai region every mounth.

  • Having monthly meeting at our office, reporting activities and planning.
  • 11
    Having activities mostly on Japan Alps once a month or every two months.

  • Having training and activities not only on weekends but also on weekdays.

    Please email us for further details.

## ### You can acquire technics and knowledge for pleasant Mountaineering. ## (GCN) ### Our club also welcomes foreign citizen who lives in Kansai region for climbing with us. Technics and experiences are not necessary to join our club. The most important thing is motivation to aim high. Will you step forward to aim high with us. Motivated Beginner is also welcomed. If you are interested in alpine style but having worry about it, you can also move to climbing division from traverse division after learning mountaineering basic skills. You will acquire safety mountaineering thoroughly. It is also possible to join training and meeting for trial. Please feel free to contact us by email We will train beginner of climbing from beginning. ## Entry condition. - - - () - Healthy person who is interested in climbing. - Experience does not matter. We will train from very beginning. - Above 18 years old to up to 55 years old. (Please ask us if you are above 55 years old) ## Membership fee | | | | |---|---|:---| |
Admission fee||8,000 |
Annual fee|
for General|6,000 | |
for Student|4,000 | |()
for married couple|10,000 | |
for Inactive member|2,000 Mountain insurance is required in each case. ### Personal Information Our club never disclose nor supply personal information in email to a third party. ** ** ** Aboout out club, admission, and trial training, please feel free to email us !!**

Page.content:
You can acquire technics and knowledge for pleasant Mountaineering.

(GCN)

Our club also welcomes foreign citizen who lives in Kansai region for climbing with us.





Technics and experiences are not necessary to join our club.
The most important thing is motivation to aim high.
Will you step forward to aim high with us.
Motivated Beginner is also welcomed.




If you are interested in alpine style but having worry about it,
you can also move to climbing division from traverse division after learning mountaineering basic skills.
You will acquire safety mountaineering thoroughly.


It is also possible to join training and meeting for trial.


Please feel free to contact us by email


We will train beginner of climbing from beginning.

Entry condition.

  • ()
  • Healthy person who is interested in climbing.
  • Experience does not matter. We will train from very beginning.
  • Above 18 years old to up to 55 years old. (Please ask us if you are above 55 years old)

Membership fee

Admission fee		 8,000

Annual fee
for General		 6,000

for Student		 4,000
()
for married couple		 10,000

for Inactive member		 2,000


Mountain insurance is required in each case.

Personal Information


Our club never disclose nor supply personal information in email to a third party.


Aboout out club, admission, and trial training, please feel free to email us !!
